I cleanly rebased and pushed to my branch. Actually there are no real conflicts, it just needs to be rebased locally and forced-pushed.

**Update**: no, actually it just looks like it works, but the result after rebasing is severely broken. I'm trying to understand what's going on.

**Update 2**: I got it. All TH* libs have been moved over in the ATen directory, I couldn't find my way anymore. Fixing.
